{"type": "article", "id": 12742, "title": "几何图形挂钩", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-29T06:36:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000227XwBnyRvQkUm2jbI5.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t从时尚圈到家居行业，简单的几何图案这几年都在大行其道。来自西班牙的设计师 Octavio Asensio 最近推出了一套几何图形挂钩，有三角形，立方体，多面体等各种形状，看上去小巧而又精致，而且 3D 的设计让墙上的挂钩即使在不挂东西的时候，也非常吸引人。圆角的设计让挂钩不会弄坏衣物等挂件，放心安全。颜色上有金色和黑色可选，可以配合不同的家居风格使用。这是<a href=\"http://www.octavioasensio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140440i519KZabCMIVzU8x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0075\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140441LSrQ3N7KF4VuldeG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7225\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140441wmcbnXguFaR8SWet.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.025\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140442nkVb4xjoFu6srQ7y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6975\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140442Uu6XevRFQd8WO40z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140443tNKkbE9gMFX1hrpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140443vFByX9MgEJtCmdI3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261404430p8tOEgIKJUZPu4v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261404443Cut7HLIYqx9cRWX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}